\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 Would you have a morning break when you'd have something?
