Well we - no, you see, by the time we'd had our breakfast it was time to get - go back - clean up the dormitories, then school. School at nine o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 Did you get a drink at playtime?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 Oh no, there was nothing at playing time, no, we used to have ten minutes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 You didn't have any milk or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 No, no. You just had - break time, you could go to the toilet, that's about all. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2182234\charrsid7304980 That\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980  right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 How about lunchtime?
