\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 What would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 Well - usually some sort of meat with a - a little green or potato, you see, and then - not every day 
but some days we used to have something afterwards, a - a pudding of some description.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 Did you ever have soup before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7891465\charrsid7304980 Oh}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980  no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 It would be like meat and two veg,?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 And some days a pudding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 About how many days a week would you get a second course?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 Twice a week, yes, about twice a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 But you usually had meat once a day every day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 That's right. Yes, yes, yes, some sort of meat. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 How about in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 What - for tea? Well it was usually bread and - bread and jam. We had bread and butter and jam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 What time would this be then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10839993\charrsid7304980 Fiveish. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 Would you have any supper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 Oh no, no supper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 No cocoa or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 Oh no. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 So you just had these }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10839993\charrsid7304980 three meals}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 Yes, three - that's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 It was more or less bread morning and evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 That's right, with a cooked meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 And this was the same Saturdays and Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 They didn't make anything different for Sunday breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 No, no, no. No, no. No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 
You mentioned that they had the band, so you'd have the necessary musical instruments. These were kept in one place, you'd have to go to a band practice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 We had - we had a ba
nd room. You see, we had a - a - we had this band room and - 'cos the band master used - it was an outside gentleman, he used to come in and - and take the boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 Come in so many times a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 Every - every day. Every day. Well - Monday to Friday. Monday to Friday.
