s. Yes. There was all the brass, they had basses, euphoniums, baritones, horns. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10839993\charrsid7304980 Then you got clarinets, oboes -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 
