\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 No, no. Any boy could join the band - if he wanted to. Yes. From choice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 You didn't have to learn?
