\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 Not ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5915702 DG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 No, no, no. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10097725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2898258\charrsid7304980 You say you'd go for a walk?
